{"tid":2107883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"認頑皮破壞交通燈 孟加拉籍中六生判18個月感化 嚴舜儀:不要令我失望　祝願你有個成功的未來","createTime":"2020-07-14T07:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T12:44:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"213e3488beb61a6f9fdb0ef8c797edf5d5357650","tid":2107883,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"去年10月13日一名17歲孟加拉籍中六生響應「18區開花」示威號召，在旺角破壞交通燈，他早前承認一項刑事損壞罪，今午於九龍城裁判法院被判18個月感化令，其間需寄宿協青社，主任裁判官嚴舜儀明言希望被告不要令其失望，更祝願他有個成功的未來。<br />\n<br />\n案發去年10月13日約傍晚6時，大批示威者在旺角聚集，部分人在九龍登打士街近彌敦道交界，用鐵通破壞交通燈。警方後來透過傳媒片段鎖定被告、即17歲孟加拉籍中六生REZA Md. Nahyan。被告警誡下承認犯案，悔懊自己行為愚蠢。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 頭條"},{"pid":"d6b9ac07c94cb90010d3a5dd58cb38d8c2be9a9f","tid":2107883,"uid":112846,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"公民民族主義已經崛起左"},{"pid":"252bb7894e282b0718e8c033f6622287d3f8d763","tid":2107883,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6b9ac07c94cb90010d3a5dd58cb38d8c2be9a9f","tid":2107883,"uid":112846,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:28:35.000Z","msg":"公民民族主義已經崛起左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad97c4c79d3ffdc5b19b2c5468c9a5c0b1e58529","tid":2107883,"uid":189157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:30:19.000Z","msg":"等睇上訴加監"},{"pid":"9ccc82d1f414fb4141b2efec0c2c60869dd8ae2a","tid":2107883,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"608dc8cfb1ed2526bbfd05e0d03fea096a46294b","tid":2107883,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote